event_data.play: Update hosts file with K8s cluster info
event_data.task: Get IP addresses for each machine

results.cmd: kubectl --kubeconfig ~/.kube/config get machines openstack-infra-control-plane-bl5vb -o json | jq -r '.status.addresses[] | select(.type=="InternalIP") | .address'
